{
  "id": "nce2-l47",
  "title": "Lesson 47: A Thirsty Ghost",
  "audio": "/audio/nce2/47ÔºçA Thirsty Ghost.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What evidence is there of a ghost?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.47,
      "endTime": 15.81
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "A public house which was recently bought by Mr.Ian Thompson is up for sale.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.82,
      "endTime": 23.78
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Mr.Thompson is going to sell it because it is haunted.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 23.79,
      "endTime": 29.62
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "He told me that he could not go to sleep one night",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 29.63,
      "endTime": 33.58
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "because he heard a strange noise coming from the bar.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.59,
      "endTime": 38.89
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The next morning,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 38.9,
      "endTime": 40.42
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "he found that the doors had been blocked by chairs and the furniture had been moved.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 40.43,
      "endTime": 47.6
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Though Mr.Thompson had turned the lights off before he went to bed,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 47.61,
      "endTime": 53.28
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "they were on in the morning.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 53.29,
      "endTime": 56.41
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He also said that he had found five empty whisky bottles",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 56.42,
      "endTime": 61.9
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "which the ghost must have drunk the night before.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.91,
      "endTime": 66.67
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When I suggested that some villagers must have come",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.68,
      "endTime": 70.56
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "in for a free drink, Mr.Thompson shook his head.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 70.57,
      "endTime": 76.51
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The villagers have told him that",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 76.52,
      "endTime": 78.78
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "they will not accept the pub even if he gives it away.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 78.79,
      "endTime": 83.79
    }
  ]
}